abstract: Exchs visits with M C Taylor

headline.main: DEAN OF CARDINALS CALLS UPON TAYLOR; Head of College Visits Hotel-- Madrid Paper Critical

lead_paragraph: ROME, Feb. 29--Gennaro Cardinal Granito Pignatelli di Belmonte, the Dean of the Sacred College, paid a courtesy call on Myron C. Taylor this afternoon in return for a simi lar visit made by the Ambassador yesterday.
